<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            color: #2C5234;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .password-box {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .warning {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="header">Summit Ridge HOA - Password Reset</h2>
        <div class="content">
            <p>A temporary password has been generated for your account.</p>
            
            <div class="password-box">
                <p><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> {{tempPassword}}</p>
            </div>

            <p>Please log in with this temporary password. For security reasons, you will be required to change it immediately upon logging in.</p>

            <p class="warning">
                If you did not request this password reset, please contact support immediately.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>